 * [http://code.google.com/p/google-summer-of-code-2007-osgeo/downloads/detail?name=Xing_Lin.tar.gz geotiff2pgraster] (PGRaster) at Google Summer of Code 2007
 * [http://svn.refractions.net/postgis/branches/gSoC2007_raster/ Code Branch]



